#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:92
msgid "Kallen"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Ranger, description=Eliomir
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:195
msgid "Eliomir"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eliomir
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Sir Gerrick, you must make it back to Kerlath Province and warn your people "
"of the danger from the south. We will lead you through the forest and clear "
"any foes from your path. You may choose some of our veterans to go with you "
"as well, and any ones you leave behind will still have time to catch up with "
"Ethiliel and Deoran."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:225
msgid ""
"With the bandits and undead vanquished behind us, what foes can there be "
"ahead? Let us hope this is a speedy journey, for the spectre of winter looms."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:231
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:302
msgid "Move Sir Gerrick to the north end of the woods"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Queen Xeila
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:262
msgid ""
"Hss... Here are the humans who have made a pact with the cursed mermen! "
"Hss..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eliomir
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:266
msgid "We have stumbled into a den of nagas!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Queen Xeila
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:270
msgid "Hss... We will kill them all, my brood. Hss..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:274
msgid ""
"We must clear this road for Deoran and Ethiliel! We must destroy the naga "
"lair!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Queen Xeila
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:280
msgid "Hss... elves! Are they friends or enemies? Hss..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:284
msgid "We are weary travelers, seeking our homes. If you but let us pass..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Queen Xeila
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:288
msgid ""
"Hss... And humans! Humans drained our swamps and made them fields for farms, "
"and now they have found my winter nest. The Land-Walkers must die! Hss..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:292
msgid ""
"She won't listen. If we leave these nagas here, they will ambush Deoran and "
"Ethiliel! We must destroy them!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:306
msgid "Defeat the Queen Xeila"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:339
msgid ""
"There are a group of naga occupying this area... they don't look very "
"friendly."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:344
msgid ""
"if they are hostile to us, they could endanger Deoran and Ethiliel as well. "
"Perhaps their leader can be reasoned with."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Queen Xeila
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:359
msgid "Hss... Who will watch over my brood now? Hss..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kramak
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:373
msgid "Ho! Me see elves. Elves tasty? Me take elves to eat."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eliomir
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:377
msgid "Err, Mr. Ogre, we are not very tasty."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kramak
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:381
msgid "Oh. Me only want tasty food. Go away."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Kramak
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:389
msgid "Wait! Me not believe you. Me eat you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Ogre
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:400
msgid "Bad food! It hurt me. Arrrrggghhhh!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Abdur
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Travelers in this desolate land! I seek that dark Sage who is rumored to "
"dwell in these lands. Surely you have come from him?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:416
msgid ""
"Indeed! I just left my comrades, who were preparing to kill the vile "
"Necromancer."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Abdur
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:420
msgid "Unworthy fools! I'll kill you for this sacrilege!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:441
msgid ""
"These naga are still in control of the road. We must clear the way for "
"Deoran and Ethiliel!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:454
msgid ""
"I will hasten back to Kerlath Province now and seek the advice of the "
"Council of Westin..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Eliomir
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:458
msgid ""
"We too will return to our councils. We have much to tell them... Much indeed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:462
msgid ""
"While the council debated the best course of action, Deoran and Ethiliel "
"prepared to enter the caves under Mebrin's fortress..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:5
msgid "The Long March"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:133
msgid "Fssth"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:136
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:140
msgid "Wizzi"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:507
msgid ""
"We have to go even further west. There are elves living to the north, and I "
"don't think they'll receive us too kindly!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:508
msgid "Come on! Hurry!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:509
msgid "Keep moving!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:510
msgid "We're almost there!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:511
msgid "Just a little further!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: race=elf
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:677
msgid "You humans have kidnaped Mebrin the Sage. You will pay for your crimes."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: description=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:681
msgid ""
"Your sage Mebrin is the criminal. He practices necromancy and has turned "
"himself into Lich. By the laws of Wesnoth, the punnishment for his crimes is "
"death!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: race=elf
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:686
msgid ""
"It is you who is a criminal and who is in a company of criminals. We will "
"not let you kill Mebrin!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: description=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:690
msgid ""
"I was a fool to waste my words on you. Prepare to meet your beloved Mebrin "
"or should I say Mal M'brin in hell, elves !"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: race=elf
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:703
msgid "Get them !"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Deoran and Urza Afalas led their men quickly from the ruins of Mal M'brin's "
"fortress..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:725
msgid "Will this forest ever end? How can we know what path to take?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:729
msgid ""
"You have to follow me! There are many false paths in these woods. Some are "
"dead ends, others are even worse!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:733
msgid "Can we trust him? His people are murderers and thieves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Minister Hylas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:737
msgid ""
"Do we have any choice? Our food is running out, and it will be winter soon..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:758
msgid ""
"This way! The only ford is a bit west of here, and the path to the north "
"will lead you into trouble!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:763
msgid ""
"I think we should head north. The road leads north, and the ford is north. "
"Why does he want us to head west?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Minister Hylas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:767
msgid ""
"Beware! I sense that there are undead monsters who have escaped Mal M'brin's "
"control running around in that area."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:773
msgid "Make your way to the north edge of the woods"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:877
msgid "Hurry! There are bandits in these woods!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:881
msgid "Why should that worry us?! Aren't you their leader?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:885
msgid "We're bandits, after all. Not all of them are loyal to me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:899
msgid "The river is just ahead!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Trapper
#. [message]: type=Poacher
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:926
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:930
msgid "The elves payed us well to kill you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: description=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:934
msgid "You bastards!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Thief
#. [message]: type=Rogue
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:938
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:942
msgid "You would have done the same to us if you were in our place!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: description=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:946
msgid "I probably would have..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:959
msgid ""
"From here you can see the banks of the river! Across it we will find the sun "
"again, and an end to these cursed trees!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:972
msgid "Urien"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:973
msgid "Jesa"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:974
msgid "Plinth"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Plinth
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:978
msgid "We cannot allow you bandits and criminals to pass through our lands!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:982
msgid "But we have slain the undead - we wish only to return to our homes!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Plinth
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:986
msgid "Nevertheless, we will have vengeance for Mebrin!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:1000
msgid "Thank heaven we have escaped that awful forest!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Gerrick
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:1004
msgid "Indeed, Afalas, you've earned my trust today."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urza Afalas
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:1008
msgid "I can only hope for mercy when I return to Westin."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06b_The_Long_March.cfg:1013
msgid "But there was a dark cloud looming behind Deoran and his men..."
msgstr ""

